{"tid":2228780,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港大保安放生藍絲撕連儂牆兼say「Thank you」被炮轟 收警告信停職兩周","createTime":"2020-10-03T23:55:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-04T02:36:49.000Z","uid":271829,"like":24,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"c5fadb3e230381834b0bb49f9956687248d19921","tid":2228780,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T23:55:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/q--Rd7Oqr8fASHGSz_qBuOgxyTA=/739x1167/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HYCOFKK3QFCQTPAMC7TF5IN6TA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fq--Rd7Oqr8fASHGSz_qBuOgxyTA%3D%2F739x1167%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHYCOFKK3QFCQTPAMC7TF5IN6TA.jpg&h=90a39836&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李梓成在facebook發帖透露，與校方管理層溝通後，校方向涉事保安發出警告信，並需要停職兩周，其間需接受訓練。<br />\n...<br />\n十多名操鄉音的藍絲上周日（27日）晚闖入港大校園，撕毀4幅連儂牆，並推到學生會旗幟，之後又闖入學生會大樓撕走玻璃門上的文宣，其間在場有多名港大保安，但任由有關人等離去，沒有阻止。事後保安被港大學生怒斥不作為，學生會亦發聲明批評保安當時僅以言語制止，阻止不力，未能保護學生，要求有關部門為失職問責。港大校委會本科生代表李梓成昨晚在facebook發帖透露，與校方管理層溝通後，校方向涉事保安發出警告信，並需要停職兩周，其間需接受訓練。<br />\n...<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201003/W6B5YHAAYNFN5OKKCVC5OPLQ2I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201003%2FW6B5YHAAYNFN5OKKCVC5OPLQ2I%2F&d=YLq6vaBnyeHQX05GIPWJdrtFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=baabbe36\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201003%2FW6B5YHAAYNFN5OKKCVC5OPLQ2I%2F&h=8e19f810\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201003/W6B5YHAAYNFN5OKKCVC5OPLQ2I/</a>"},{"pid":"e9f76c9df5a0ddfd88d9f28236176cc85424476f","tid":2228780,"uid":36901,"like":35,"dislike":2,"score":33,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T00:00:50.000Z","msg":"舉售指公,say thank you?<br />\n直頭係共犯黎啦<br />\n串謀刑毀<br />\n煽動罪呀"},{"pid":"b49638fbbf552fcf502d6cba49b4d6972123b980","tid":2228780,"uid":3741